          "settings": {
            "liquid": "<style>\n  .klip-review {\n    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;\n    max-width: 520px;\n    padding: 28px 32px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(44, 26, 21, 0.07);\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__stars {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 3px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__stars svg {\n    width: 22px;\n    height: 22px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__trustpilot {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__trustpilot-logo {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 5px;\n  }\n\n  /* Trustpilot star icon */\n  .tp-star {\n    width: 18px;\n    height: 18px;\n    background: #00b67a;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .tp-star svg {\n    width: 11px;\n    height: 11px;\n    fill: #fff;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__trustpilot-text {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #aaa;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__trustpilot-text span {\n    color: #191919;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__body {\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: #2c1a15;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin-bottom: 18px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__footer {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__avatar {\n    width: 32px;\n    height: 32px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5c9bc, #e8a090);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: #fff;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__author {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    color: #2c1a15;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__date {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: #aaa;\n    margin-left: auto;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__verified {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 4px;\n    font-size: 11.5px;\n    color: #00b67a;\n    font-weight: 400;\n  }\n\n  .klip-review__verified svg {\n    width: 12px;\n    height: 12px;\n    stroke: #00b67a;\n    fill: none;\n    stroke-width: 2.5;\n    stroke-linecap: round;\n    stroke-linejoin: round;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"klip-faq\">\n\n  <!-- Item 1 : All hair types -->\n  <div class=\"klip-faq__item\">\n    <button class=\"klip-faq__trigger\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__trigger-left\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"klip-faq__title\">Fonctionne-t-elle sur tous les types de cheveux ?</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__arrow\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg>\n      </div>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"klip-faq__body\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <p>Oui. VELVY™ est conçue pour tous les types de cheveux, sans exception. Le secret : il suffit d'ajuster la quantité de cheveux que vous prenez dans la pince.</p>\n          <div class=\"klip-hair-grid\">\n            <div class=\"klip-hair-card\">\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__title\">Cheveux fins</div>\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__body\">Vous pouvez prendre une mèche plus généreuse — l'aimant tient sans écraser ni tirer les cheveux. Fini les réajustements toutes les cinq minutes.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"klip-hair-card\">\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__title\">Cheveux épais</div>\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__body\">Prenez une mèche plus petite pour que l'aimant se referme correctement. La force aimantée s'adapte à votre densité et tient toute la journée sans effort.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"klip-hair-card\">\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__title\">Cheveux bouclés &amp; texturés</div>\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__body\">Aucun ressort qui accroche ou tire sur vos boucles. Le système aimanté tient sans à-coups, vos boucles restent intactes.</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"klip-hair-card\">\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__title\">Cheveux raides</div>\n              <div class=\"klip-hair-card__body\">L'aimant assure une fermeture ferme même sur les cheveux les plus glissants. Elle ne se desserre pas, elle ne tombe pas.</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Item 2 : Specifications -->\n  <div class=\"klip-faq__item\">\n    <button class=\"klip-faq__trigger\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__trigger-left\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"8\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"18\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"6\" x2=\"3.01\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"3.01\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"18\" x2=\"3.01\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"klip-faq__title\">Caractéristiques</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__arrow\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg>\n      </div>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"klip-faq__body\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <ul>\n            <li>Taille : <strong>3 cm par partie</strong> (2 pièces)</li>\n            <li>Fermeture : <strong>aimantée</strong></li>\n            <li>Design : <strong>ultra plat</strong></li>\n            <li>Compatible avec : <strong>tous les types de cheveux</strong></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Item 3 : Shipping -->\n  <div class=\"klip-faq__item\">\n    <button class=\"klip-faq__trigger\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__trigger-left\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect x=\"1\" y=\"3\" width=\"15\" height=\"13\" rx=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M16 8h4l3 3v5h-7V8z\"></path><circle cx=\"5.5\" cy=\"18.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle><circle cx=\"18.5\" cy=\"18.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"klip-faq__title\">Expédition & livraison</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__arrow\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg>\n      </div>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"klip-faq__body\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <p>Expédié sous <strong>48 heures</strong>. Une fois expédiée, les délais de livraison estimés sont :</p>\n          <div class=\"klip-delivery-grid\">\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇬🇧 Royaume-Uni</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇮🇪 Irlande</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇫🇷 France</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇩🇪 Allemagne</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇺🇸 États-Unis</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇦🇺 Australie</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇨🇦 Canada</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🇳🇿 Nouvelle-Zélande</span><span>7 – 14 jours</span></div>\n            <div class=\"klip-delivery-row\"><span>🌍 Reste du monde</span><span>7 – 20 jours</span></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Item 4 : Ce qui nous différencie -->\n  <div class=\"klip-faq__item\">\n    <button class=\"klip-faq__trigger\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__trigger-left\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"klip-faq__title\">Ce qui nous différencie</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__arrow\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg>\n      </div>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"klip-faq__body\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <p>La pince à cheveux n'avait pas évolué depuis plus de <strong>125 ans</strong>. VELVY™ a tout repensé. Son <strong>design aimanté ultra-plat en deux parties</strong> transforme votre façon d'attacher vos cheveux : posez, clippez, c'est fait en deux secondes.</p>\n          <p>Grâce à sa forme totalement plate, VELVY™ ne crée aucune bosse derrière la tête — vous pouvez vous adosser, conduire, faire du sport ou vous allonger sans jamais la sentir.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Item 5 : Built to last -->\n  <div class=\"klip-faq__item\">\n    <button class=\"klip-faq__trigger\" aria-expanded=\"false\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__trigger-left\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__icon\">\n          <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"klip-faq__title\">Conçue pour durer</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__arrow\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg>\n      </div>\n    </button>\n    <div class=\"klip-faq__body\">\n      <div class=\"klip-faq__body-inner\">\n        <div class=\"klip-faq__content\">\n          <p>VELVY™ est conçue pour être <strong>la pince que vous n'aurez jamais à remplacer</strong>. Sans ressort fragile ni plastique qui casse, son système aimanté plat résiste aux ouvertures répétées, aux chutes au sol et aux journées entières de port.</p>\n          <p>Résultat : une pince quasi incassable qui conserve sa tenue et sa forme très longtemps.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.querySelectorAll('.klip-faq__trigger').forEach(function(trigger) {\n    trigger.addEventListener('click', function() {\n      var item = this.closest('.klip-faq__item');\n      var isOpen = item.classList.contains('is-open');\n      document.querySelectorAll('.klip-faq__item').forEach(function(el) {\n        el.classList.remove('is-open');\n        el.querySelector('.klip-faq__trigger').setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');\n      });\n      if (!isOpen) {\n        item.classList.add('is-open');\n        trigger.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>"
